{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-107-108-it-s-too-small",
    "title": "Lesson 107: It's too small.",
    "audioFilename": "107&108－It's Too Small..mp3",
    "duration": 103.158,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.43,
      "end": 2.25,
      "text": "Lesson 107.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第107课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 3.97,
      "end": 5.61,
      "text": "It's Too Small.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "太小了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 7.59,
      "end": 11.77,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 13.45,
      "end": 16.63,
      "text": "What kind of dress does the lady want?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这位女士想要什么样的连衣裙？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 19.21,
      "end": 22.05,
      "text": "Do you like this dress, madam?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "女士，您喜欢这件连衣裙吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 23.15,
      "end": 26.13,
      "text": "I like the color very much.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我非常喜欢这个颜色。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 26.13,
      "end": 31.91,
      "text": "It's a lovely dress, but it's too small for me.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这件连衣裙很漂亮，但对我来说太小了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 33.15,
      "end": 35.03,
      "text": "What about this one?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这件怎么样？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 35.75,
      "end": 37.47,
      "text": "It's a lovely dress.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这件连衣裙很漂亮。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 38.33,
      "end": 40.07,
      "text": "It's very smart.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "也很时髦。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 41.43,
      "end": 43.89,
      "text": "Short skirts are in fashion now.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "现在流行短裙。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 44.69,
      "end": 46.71,
      "text": "Would you like to try it?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您想试穿一下吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 47.71,
      "end": 48.35,
      "text": "All right.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "好吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 49.35,
      "end": 56.29,
      "text": "I'm afraid this green dress is too small for me as well.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "恐怕这件绿色连衣裙对我来说也太小了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 57.91,
      "end": 61.07,
      "text": "It's smaller than the blue one.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "它比那件蓝色的还小。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 62.19,
      "end": 65.25,
      "text": "I don't like the color, either.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我也不喜欢这个颜色。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 66.13,
      "end": 69.11,
      "text": "It doesn't suit me at all.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "它一点也不适合我。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 70.03,
      "end": 73.55,
      "text": "I think the blue dress is prettier.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我觉得那件蓝色连衣裙更漂亮。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 74.51,
      "end": 78.19,
      "text": "Could you show me another blue dress?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您能再给我看一件蓝色连衣裙吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 79.11,
      "end": 85.39,
      "text": "I want a dress like that one, but it must be my size.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我想要一件那样的，但必须是我的尺码。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 87.23,
      "end": 91.61,
      "text": "I'm afraid I haven't got a larger dress.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "恐怕我没有更大的连衣裙了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 92.61,
      "end": 96.31,
      "text": "This is the largest dress in the shop.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这是店里最大的一件。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
